Odoo & ERP Administration :

Installed, configured, and managed Odoo in testing and production environments.

Deployed and managed custom Odoo modules across multiple environments.

Implemented Odoo worker configuration and optimized memory parameters (limit_memory_soft, limit_memory_hard) for performance tuning.

Performed production troubleshooting and performance optimization for ERP systems.


PostgreSQL Database Administration :

Configured and tuned PostgreSQL parameters based on Odoo worker architecture.

Implemented automated database backups using cron jobs and validated restore procedures.

Configured PgBouncer for connection pooling and optimized database connection handling.

Implemented basic streaming replication setup and configured WAL archiving.

Performed Point-in-Time Recovery (PITR) testing and demonstrated disaster recovery scenarios.


Web & Infrastructure Management :

Deployed and configured NGINX as a reverse proxy for Odoo in local, testing, and production environments.

Managed environment separation (development, testing, production) for ERP deployments.

Ensured high availability and performance optimization at the web and database layers.


Monitoring & Observability :

Installed and configured Prometheus for system and database monitoring.

Designed dashboards in Grafana to visualize server, PostgreSQL, and application metrics.

Monitored CPU, memory, disk I/O, and database performance metrics to ensure production stability.


Containerization & Automation :

Demonstrated containerized deployment of Odoo using Docker.

Automated routine maintenance tasks using cron jobs and shell scripting.

Maintained Linux servers ensuring uptime, security updates, and system performance optimization.
